ernal autonumber" title="http://www.mcfarlandpub.com/excerpts/0-7864-1320-4.Chapter7.pdf" rel="nofollow">[7]</a> and <i>Judgment by Film: Socio-Legal Functions of Rashomon</i> by Orit Kamir <a href="http://sitemaker.umich.edu/Orit_Kamir/files/rashomon.pdf" class="external autonumber" title="http://sitemaker.umich.edu/Orit_Kamir/files/rashomon.pdf" rel="nofollow">[8]</a>.</li>
